  "id": "php/addarrayitems",
  "contentHtml": "<h1>Add Array Item</h1>\n<p>For indexed arrays:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use the bracket syntax.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For associative arrays:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use brackets for the key, and assign value with the = operator.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$fruits</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Apple'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Orange'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Banana'</span>];\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$fruits</span>[] = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Cherry\"</span>;\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$vegetables</span> = [\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Kale\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">12</span>,\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Spinach\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>\r\n];\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$vegetables</span>[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Broccoli\"</span>] = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>;\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Add Multiple Array Items</h2>\n<p>For indexed arrays:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use the array_push() function.\r\nFor associative arrays:</li>\n<li>Use the += operator.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$fruits</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Apple\"</span>];\r\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">array_push</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$fruits</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Banana\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Cherry\"</span>);\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$vegetables</span> = [\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Kale\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">12</span>\r\n];\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$vegetables</span> += [\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Spinach\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>,\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Broccoli\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>\r\n];\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>",
